We did it! 

We found Connor McDavid’s biggest fan! 

Meet Recchi Robichaud, a 14–year-old from New Brunswick, that has collected almost 500 hockey cards featuring NHL superstar @mcdavid97 🤯

The Baie-Sainte-Anne teen used his downtime during the pandemic to more than double the number of McDavid cards he had back in the summer of 2020 

Robichaud was born to be a hockey super fan and was even named after one of his dad’s favourite NHL players—Mark Recchi

Read more about how Robichaud grew his collection at the link in our bio 

H/t: @cbcnewbrunswick & @cbcedmonton
